news.title: Provident Housing secures Rs 1,150 crore investment from HDFC Capital
news.para: Provident Housing and HDFC Capital collaboration will add an additional 6.2 million sq ft of new residential projects with a combined gross development value (GDV) of Rs 17,100 crore.

news.title: ACC posts net profit of Rs 944.84 crore in Q4 FY24
news.para: ACC's net consolidated total income stood at Rs 5,528.45 crore, a growth of 12.59 per cent from Rs 4,910.06 crore it recorded in the similar quarter last year.

news.title: Three people booked for duping developer over sale of land in Thane
news.para: The builder alleged that he and his family paid Rs 42 lakh to the accused in connection with the deal but the accused neither got the land transferred nor refunded the money.

news.title: Anant Raj's net profit up 73.43% in Q4 FY24
news.para: Anant Raj's net consolidated total income stood at Rs 453.12 crore, a growth of 56.31 per cent from Rs 289.89 crore it recorded in the similar quarter last year.

news.title: Edelweiss Alternatives' RYP Fund completes acquisition of MMTP Projects for over Rs 1,500 crore
news.para: RYP fund's portfolio has scaled up to 1.8 million sq ft gross leasable area (GLA) in Bengaluru and Gurugram. With this acquisition, RYP currently holds assets valued over Rs 2,500 crore.

news.title: Sumadhura Group acquires 40 acres land for about Rs 800 crore in Bengaluru
news.para: Sumadhura Group plans to develop four residential projects on these sites - three in the east and one in south west Bengaluru over the next five years with an estimated potential of six million sq ft of saleable area.

news.title: Macrotech Developers' net profit dips 10.61% in Q4 FY24
news.para: Macrotech Developers' net consolidated total income stood at Rs 4,083.90 crore, a growth of 24.83 per cent from Rs 3,271.70 crore it recorded in the similar quarter last year.

news.title: Buyer sentiment strong in housing segment, says Magicbricks survey
news.para: The real estate platform unveiled its flagship Housing Sentiment Index (HSI) report, reflecting a positive outlook for the residential real estate market, with an overall HSI of 149.

news.title: ED raids Tulsiani Group as part of money laundering investigation
news.para: An office premise in the Gomti Nagar area of Lucknow, linked to a family member of BJP MLA from Harraiya (Basti) Ajay Singh, was also covered by the agency as part of the probe against the Tulsiani Group.

news.title: Dalmia Bharat's net profit dips 47.37% in Q4 FY24
news.para: Dalmia Bharat's net consolidated total income stood at Rs 4,427 crore in Q4 FY24, a growth of 11.99 per cent from Rs 3,953 crore it recorded in the similar quarter last year.

news.title: US judge approves $418 million antitrust settlement against National Association of Realtors
news.para: U.S. District Judge Stephen Bough's settlement order marked a key first step in a months-long process that will culminate in a final approval hearing set for Nov. 26 in Kansas City, Missouri.

news.title: Country Garden gets bondholders' approval to postpone payments of three onshore bonds
news.para: The largest Chinese private developer, which has defaulted on its $11 billion offshore bonds and is working on an offshore debt restructuring plan, had in September extended the maturities of eight onshore bonds worth 10.8 billion yuan.

news.title: New home sales increase 8.8% in USA in March 2024
news.para: The report from the Commerce Department on Tuesday also showed the median house price jumped to a seven month-high from February, likely as fewer builders offered price cuts and sales shifted to higher priced homes.

news.title: REITs, InvITs mobilise Rs 1.3 lakh crore in four years: RBI data
news.para: Experts and stakeholders are of the view that with India growing at a fast pace, REITs and InvITs are emerging as alternative investment instruments, especially for high net-worth individuals.

news.title: Kolkata civic body to upload all information about buildings on portal
news.para: The municipal commissioner, Dhaval Jain, has asked the buildings department officials to prepare a ward-wise list of unauthorized buildings and upload the same on the KMC website for the benefit of potential flat-buyers.

news.title: Bihar REAT hindered by lack of quorum, raises concerns over 'illegal' appointments
news.para: The tribunal, however, could not pass an order as it lacked quorum. This was the second such case in the past one week when the tribunal could not pass an order for the same reason.

news.title: WeWork founder wants bankruptcy court's help in bid to repurchase company
news.para: Adam Neumann's new real estate company, Flow Global, has sought to buy WeWork out of bankruptcy, recently offering over $500 million.
